sub_title: Pilot, Flight Safety Officer, Technical Ground/ CRM Instructor
summary:
Profile: Aviator, Maritime and Offshore Logistic background, with 12.000 total flight hours.
Verifiable record of non-FAA or JAA violations, no criminal history. Solid training record. 
Facilitate open communication and mutual respect among all work groups. 
Committed to Flight Safety First
Firm advocate of Crew Resource management .

Specialties: Management, Flight and Simulator Training, Crew Resource Management  and Aviation Psychology.

Founder of Base Online B.V.
Providing the market with Aviation and Maritime Services, licensing, training and logistical  support.
